title: Practice, anti-practice, and meta-practice cycles: reincarnation within a lifetime.
description:
The amazing Rick Repetti returns.  We discuss dialogos, philosophical fellowship, and then we discuss Rick's replies to comments made by Paul Vanderklay to my previous discussions with Rick.
